phrases: We will now begin the 57th expedition beyond the walls!
We believe that in the basement of Eren Jaeger's Zhiganshina home,
there are answers about the Titans that he himself does not have.
You new recruits will be here.
You will be between the cart guard team
Your job will be to ride alongside the spare horses and relay messages.
The Special Operations Squad will be here.
Standing by in the center of the last ranks.
It is the safest place in the formation.
We are even better protected than the supply carts.
Like the Armored or Colossal Titans, or Eren...
A human in the body of a Titan!
Its movements are much more precise than the others' are!
Avenge the bastard who rushed to his death!
That is the one that killed him!
He rushed to his death on the right flank!
We have bought enough time, right?
Let us get the hell away from it!
Forest of Giant Trees 57th Expedition Beyond the Walls (2)
How is your 3D Maneuver Gear looking, Armin?
The clasp released as intended, so it seems it is not broken.
I am glad to hear it.
If Jean's horse comes back, the three of us can move, but...
Reiner's horse returned, so why did not mine?
We cannot stay here any longer.
In the worst case, we will have to leave someone here...
But how would we decide who to leave?
Reiner, since he is big and would have trouble riding with someone else?
Or should I run and try to find my horse?
Why the hell do I have to think about this?!
We all made it through that fight alive.
Are you still out of it?
Yeah, my head's still a bit fuzzy...
It is a hard choice, but someone will have to stay behind.
First, let us fire a smoke round...
If the formation continued straight ahead,
the row 4-3 team should be nearby.
That is the signal for an emergency...
But I cannot imagine they will understand our intentions just from that.
Armin, we can wait another three minutes.
But there is something I want you to tell them for me...
I cannot believe that smoke round brought you here.
I was nearby, and I already had Jean's horse.
It seems you have a strange charisma.
that the worst did not happen to you.
Well, we should rejoin the formation as soon as possible.
Yeah, there should be orders to retreat.
To think we have been pushed back, less than an hour out of the walls.
Things are even bleaker than I would imagined...
it went in the opposite direction from the vanguard command team...
Looks like they are continuing the operation,
That was not a retreat command?
In theory, any soldier has the authority to determine
when mission completion is no longer possible.
Did command not see our smoke round somehow?
Even if we do not know what is going on,
there is still only one thing for us to do...
For now, everything seems to be going fine.
We may already have casualties on the front lines.
Right flank recon has been destroyed!
Our recon system is partially inoperative.
Pass this on, to the left.
I think that is where Armin is.
But Armin and the others should still be in position, near the center.
The Titans cannot have made it in that far...
We let it penetrate deep into our formation.
Beneath those smoke rounds, is there someone fighting?
You are pretty smart, but you cannot possibly protect all three targets!
Hit one, and we will slow it down...
Damn you for causing so many deaths!
We will make you die a slow, painful death!
The most important thing is to ensure they hear of this...
I must tell them what we are up against!
It got in all the way here?
We cannot let it penetrate any farther!
The right flank's been wiped out?
Just relay the message to the left!
Our goal is supposed to be south, to the old city.
Right now, our formation's on a collision course.
Forest of Giant Trees (1) Isolated forests of giant trees can be found within and beyond the walls.
They occur naturally in certain areas, and tree heights can exceed 80 meters.
Forest of Giant Trees (2) Before Wall Maria's fall, this particular forest was a tourist area.
Now, it is a strategically important location used by the Survey Corps to protect themselves from Titans during expeditions.
There is nothing growing on the road.
We can bring the carts through, too.
that only the central cart guard should enter the forest.
The center row appears to be entering the forest,
but would not the rest of us collide with the forest?
Hey, what are we doing at this tourist spot?
We are totally off from both our original destination and our return point.
I do not know, but the order came from Commander Erwin, after all.
for us new recruits at a tourist spot?
No, I do not think so.
Anyway, that giant woman's following us.
No matter what his plan, we cannot stay here.
The only thing I can imagine
is that we are passing through on our way to somewhere else...
We will now make preparations to launch a counterattack.
Draw your blades, and wait above in the trees.
If any Titans try to enter this forest, stop them at all costs!
H-Hey, it looks like only the center line went into the woods.
The forest blocks our advance, so the left and right flanks
will have to skirt the forest.
We have lost our recon ability.
Why did not we change course to avoid this forest?
Did Commander Erwin read the map wrong?
Perhaps we tried too hard to avoid the threat
on the right flank and ended up here...
We have abandoned the original mission to cache supplies.
And when we abandoned it, we should have turned tail and run...
But instead, we are forging ahead to a tourist trap.
And now, we are just standing here,
to stop any Titans that enter the woods?
Damn him for giving a crazy order.
And this no real explanation thing is innovative, too.
Of course, I am sure he has his own concerns...
A commander deemed worthless by his men in a critical situation
quite often succumbs to a mysterious attack from behind.
I am just saying it would not surprise me.
Jean, so what are you going to do?
This situation's got me a bit worked up, that is all.
What am I going to do?
Obey my orders, and keep Titans out of the forest.
You also think it is the right move, do not you?
You look like you know something.
No, that is not what we should think about.
The Female Titan is pursuing Eren.
Assume those two things, and see what you can deduce...
We are in the middle of the woods!
we will not know if Titans are approaching!
It seems something is approaching us from the right...
How are we supposed to dodge the Titans or protect the carts?
Do not go on and on about the obvious...
We cannot do that anymore, of course.
It is the perfect environment for 3D Maneuver Gear.
And try to use that tiny brain of yours...
If you do not want to die, think.
I just cannot keep up right now because I am still new.
He will not just tell me the answer.
I have to figure it out for myself.
I am sure that is how they all learned to fight.
What the hell is going on here?
No one knows what is really going on?
The Female Titan is after Eren...
If I am right about that,
then there is only one reason to come here.
This is where Commander Erwin intends to deal with the Female Titan...
Our orders were to keep the Titans out of the forest, right?
There is no longer any reason to fight...
It is from directly behind us!
It is whatever was coming toward us on the right.
If we see it, it will only be for a second.
In these trees, there is no way to foresee and evade its attacks!
Captain, let us switch to Maneuver Gear!
Fool, you have run straight into hell.
You are chasing a group of master Titan killers!
At this rate, it will catch up with us!
That is why we came to this forest!
The Female Titan continues its pursuit, leaving carnage in its wake.
Despite witnessing their friends get slaughtered
before their very eyes, the Survey Corps can only flee.
Eren is faced with a decision.
